reviewText: I enjoyed the product. It was what I expected.
Regardless of the other reviews I really enjoyed this movie a lot and its packed full of action and so much more and its worth buying
Loved this movie!  Great love story with a happy ending!

If you want an ancient love story then this would be a good movie for you. If you want a good action story then look for Duane Johnson's Hercules, which has a better plot and a group of fighters who deserve to have action figures if they don't already have them.
